{"tid":2349724,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇港島區salon推介？","createTime":"2021-01-01T18:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T01:06:04.000Z","uid":283071,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c41ae497e61ebc2838b7ef79313dfbe2be1c51","tid":2349724,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"我已經好耐冇剪過頭髮 跪求介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔鍾意同髮型師吹水<br />\n最好唔好講野 <br />\n所以好少重複幫襯同一間salon超過3次<br />\n怕佢地以為熟左係咁撩我講野<br />\n<br />\n對上剪個間 <br />\n環境幾好 有餅乾食有咖啡飲<br />\n本身都諗住可以幫襯第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知洗頭條女又撩我吹水 想訓下都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剪頭髮條友撩我講政治<br />\n一開波講就話香港搞成咁好慘<br />\n我冇咩答佢 佢仲自己係度鳩嗡 <br />\n講講下原來條友藍既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"856ec62b7f1a6f2775293b2ce336c29d8d5e8726","tid":2349724,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T20:38:13.000Z","msg":"是但啦去速剪差唔多"},{"pid":"9e20273a3494805e3c97b6c8fbeaa36ba9125230","tid":2349724,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"856ec62b7f1a6f2775293b2ce336c29d8d5e8726","tid":2349724,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T20:38:13.000Z","msg":"是但啦去速剪差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T01:42:58.000Z","msg":"男 <br />\n速剪應該剷草咁剪 我唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d817746291d78d8937556dac27b3c9efb98d47","tid":2349724,"uid":260866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"彌賽亞髮廊<br />\n灣仔駱克道357號<br />\n2891 7569<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/maps/cZVmcq7UWFcAbDHz9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fmaps%2FcZVmcq7UWFcAbDHz9&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gVQYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=8c6b9252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/maps/cZVmcq7U